   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PROMOTE LIVELIHOOD THROUGH DIGNIFIED MENSTRUATION</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Effective solutions to improve menstrual health is still lacking in Nepal, while ignorance and false perceptions continue to exist. Women still face restrictions during their mensuration in terms of eating, space, mobility, touch.  The project is looking to promote livelihood through dignified menstruation in conjunction with MITERI bio-degradable pad enterprise. Coupled with health education and advocacy, your support for this project will also provide girls eco-friendly sanitary pads.</narrative>
  </description>
